---
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Issue 47 — GTM Triggers Weekly"
  description="Sample issue of GTM Triggers Weekly. Real triggers ranked by TVA. Hiring velocity, AI penetration, funded-and-hiring, stack moves, and the trigger of the week."
  path="/newsletter/sample/"
>
  <div class="bg-grid" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <main>
    <section class="section sample-section">
      <div class="container">

        <!-- Breadcrumb back to newsletter -->
        <a href="/newsletter/" class="sample-back">
          <span class="sample-back__arrow">←</span>
          Back to newsletter
        </a>

        <!-- The issue -->
        <article class="issue">

          <!-- Masthead -->
          <header class="issue__head">
            <div class="issue__masthead">
              <div class="issue__masthead-left">
                <span class="issue__masthead-name">GTM Triggers Weekly</span>
                <span class="issue__masthead-sub">A subagent/gtm publication</span>
              </div>
              <div class="issue__masthead-right">
                <span class="issue__num">ISSUE 47</span>
                <span class="issue__date">May 14, 2026</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="issue__intro">
              <span class="issue__intro-label">THIS WEEK</span>
              <p class="issue__intro-body">
                Marketing crossed the <strong>17%</strong> AI-penetration line for the first time.
                <strong>412 funded companies</strong> just opened their first VP Sales role. And at
                twenty-three mid-market SaaS companies, Apollo got ripped out and Clay went in.
              </p>
            </div>
          </header>

          <!-- Section 01: Hiring velocity -->
          <section class="issue__section">
            <div class="issue__section-head">
              <span class="issue__section-num">01 /</span>
              <h2 class="issue__section-title">Hiring velocity watch</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="issue__section-desc">
              Series A–C SaaS with three or more senior engineering roles posted in the last
              fourteen days. Forward-rate spikes likely two to three weeks out.
            </p>

            <div class="rows">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="row__main">
                  <span class="row__name">Cresta</span>
                  <span class="row__note">Four senior backend roles plus one staff AI/ML. All Bay Area.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row__meta">
                  <span class="row__stage">SERIES C</span>
                  <span class="row__stat">5 ROLES · 9d</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="row__main">
                  <span class="row__name">Hex</span>
                  <span class="row__note">Three senior frontend, one staff PM, one head of platform.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row__meta">
                  <span class="row__stage">SERIES B</span>
                  <span class="row__stat">5 ROLES · 11d</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="row__main">
                  <span class="row__name">Hightouch</span>
                  <span class="row__note">Five senior engineering roles, all React/Node. Largest open burst since Series B.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row__meta">
                  <span class="row__stage">SERIES B</span>
                  <span class="row__stat">5 ROLES · 6d</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="row__main">
                  <span class="row__name">Stytch</span>
                  <span class="row__note">Three platform engineers plus first DevRel hire.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row__meta">
                  <span class="row__stage">SERIES B</span>
                  <span class="row__stat">4 ROLES · 13d</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="issue__section-caption">
              Velocity above three roles in fourteen days correlates with a Q+1 GTM hiring wave.
              Watch for VP Sales/Marketing posts at these companies in the next 30–60 days.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Section 02: AI penetration -->
          <section class="issue__section">
            <div class="issue__section-head">
              <span class="issue__section-num">02 /</span>
              <h2 class="issue__section-title">AI penetration movers</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="issue__section-desc">
              Functions that crossed +0.3ppt week-over-week. Source: AI Penetration Index, 27,000+ active postings.
            </p>

            <div class="bars">
              <div class="bars__row">
                <span class="bars__label">Marketing</span>
                <div class="bars__track"><div class="bars__fill" style="width: 86%"></div></div>
                <span class="bars__pct">17.1%</span>
                <span class="bars__delta">↑ +0.9</span>
              </div>
              <div class="bars__row">
                <span class="bars__label">Operations</span>
                <div class="bars__track"><div class="bars__fill" style="width: 62%"></div></div>
                <span class="bars__pct">12.4%</span>
                <span class="bars__delta">↑ +0.5</span>
              </div>
              <div class="bars__row">
                <span class="bars__label">Legal</span>
                <div class="bars__track"><div class="bars__fill" style="width: 64%"></div></div>
                <span class="bars__pct">12.7%</span>
                <span class="bars__delta">↑ +0.4</span>
              </div>
              <div class="bars__row">
                <span class="bars__label">Sales</span>
                <div class="bars__track"><div class="bars__fill" style="width: 55%"></div></div>
                <span class="bars__pct">10.9%</span>
                <span class="bars__delta">↑ +0.3</span>
              </div>
              <div class="bars__row">
                <span class="bars__label">People/HR</span>
                <div class="bars__track"><div class="bars__fill" style="width: 31%"></div></div>
                <span class="bars__pct">6.1%</span>
                <span class="bars__delta">↑ +0.3</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="issue__section-caption">
              Marketing is the inflection point. CMOs hiring against AI-fluent JDs at scale for
              the first time. The salary premium for Marketing roles mentioning AI is now
              <strong>+$28,400</strong>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Section 03: Funded + hiring -->
          <section class="issue__section">
            <div class="issue__section-head">
              <span class="issue__section-num">03 /</span>
              <h2 class="issue__section-title">Funded and hiring</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="issue__section-desc">
              Series A/B/C raised in the last 90 days that just opened their first VP Sales or Head of GTM role.
            </p>

            <div class="rows">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="row__main">
                  <span class="row__name">Vellum AI</span>
                  <span class="row__note">VP Sales open eight days. First commercial leadership hire.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row__meta">
                  <span class="row__stage">SERIES A · $20M</span>
                  <span class="row__stat">OPEN 8d</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="row__main">
                  <span class="row__name">Modal Labs</span>
                  <span class="row__note">VP Sales open fourteen days. PLG founder team hiring sales for first time.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row__meta">
                  <span class="row__stage">SERIES B · $80M</span>
                  <span class="row__stat">OPEN 14d</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="row__main">
                  <span class="row__name">Distyl AI</span>
                  <span class="row__note">Head of GTM open four days. Forward-deployed model — selling to F500.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row__meta">
                  <span class="row__stage">SEED · $32M</span>
                  <span class="row__stat">OPEN 4d</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Conversion bridge — only one per issue -->
            <div class="bridge">
              <div class="bridge__label">SUBSCRIBERS ASK</div>
              <p class="bridge__body">
                "Can you filter this to only the companies in <em>my</em> ICP?" — Yes. The
                ICP-filtered tier ships in June. <a href="/contact/">Reply to this email</a> to
                be on the early list.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Section 04: Stack moves -->
          <section class="issue__section">
            <div class="issue__section-head">
              <span class="issue__section-num">04 /</span>
              <h2 class="issue__section-title">Stack moves</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="issue__section-desc">
              Tools added or removed in the last fourteen days at mid-market SaaS companies.
              Detected via BuiltWith and Wappalyzer signal pulls.
            </p>

            <ul class="stacklist">
              <li>
                <span class="stacklist__strike">Apollo</span>
                <span class="stacklist__arrow">→</span>
                <span class="stacklist__add">Clay</span>
                <span class="stacklist__note">at twenty-three companies. Largest stack-swap of the quarter.</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="stacklist__strike">ZoomInfo</span>
                <span class="stacklist__arrow">→</span>
                <span class="stacklist__add">enrichment + LinkedIn Sales Nav</span>
                <span class="stacklist__note">at eleven companies. Cost cuts, not capability cuts.</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="stacklist__add">Common Room</span>
                <span class="stacklist__note">added at eight companies — replacing</span>
                <span class="stacklist__strike">Mutiny</span>
                <span class="stacklist__note">in five of them.</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="stacklist__add">HubSpot Breeze</span>
                <span class="stacklist__note">activated at fourteen companies — most still in pilot.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>

            <p class="issue__section-caption">
              Stack churn is a buying signal. Tools getting ripped out are tells about which
              categories are losing trust this quarter.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Section 05: Trigger of the week -->
          <section class="issue__section">
            <div class="issue__section-head">
              <span class="issue__section-num">05 /</span>
              <h2 class="issue__section-title">Trigger of the week</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="featured">
              <span class="featured__badge">
                <span class="featured__badge-dot"></span>
                HIGHEST TVA SCORE THIS WEEK
              </span>

              <h3 class="featured__title">The Practice Ownership Change Trigger</h3>

              <p class="featured__lede">
                <strong>Forty-seven healthcare practices</strong> changed ownership in the last
                thirty days. Each new owner is in the ninety-day window where every tech stack
                decision gets re-opened — EHR, billing, RCM, marketing, patient comms. The
                trigger fires once per practice and decays fast.
              </p>

              <div class="featured__sta">
                <div class="featured__sta-row">
                  <span class="featured__sta-label">SPECIFIC</span>
                  <div class="featured__sta-track"><div class="featured__sta-fill" style="width: 100%"></div></div>
                  <span class="featured__sta-val">3/3</span>
                </div>
                <div class="featured__sta-row">
                  <span class="featured__sta-label">TIMELY</span>
                  <div class="featured__sta-track"><div class="featured__sta-fill" style="width: 100%"></div></div>
                  <span class="featured__sta-val">3/3</span>
                </div>
                <div class="featured__sta-row">
                  <span class="featured__sta-label">ACTIONABLE</span>
                  <div class="featured__sta-track"><div class="featured__sta-fill" style="width: 100%"></div></div>
                  <span class="featured__sta-val">3/3</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="featured__more">
                Full Trigger → Asset walkthrough — including the calculator we built for a
                healthcare RCM customer last quarter — in the June 11 issue.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Issue footer -->
          <footer class="issue__foot">
            <div class="issue__foot-tag">
              subagent<span class="issue__foot-slash">/</span>gtm — Built. Operated. Owned.
            </div>
            <p class="issue__foot-pitch">
              We turn triggers into outbound that ops teams forward.
            </p>
            <div class="issue__foot-meta">
              <a href="https://subagentgtm.com">subagentgtm.com</a>
              <span>·</span>
              <a href="/methodology/">Read the TVA framework</a>
              <span>·</span>
              <a href="/contact/">Book a build</a>
            </div>
          </footer>

        </article>

        <!-- Sub-issue CTA: subscribe to get the next one -->
        <aside class="sample-cta">
          <h2 class="sample-cta__title">Get the next one in your inbox.</h2>
          <p class="sample-cta__sub">Issue 48 ships next Wednesday. Free, weekly, unsubscribe anytime.</p>
          <form class="nl-form nl-form--centered" id="sample-signup" novalidate>
            <input
              type="email"
              class="nl-form__field"
              name="email"
              placeholder="you@company.com"
              aria-label="Email address"
              required
            />
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary btn--large nl-form__btn">
              Subscribe →
            </button>
          </form>
        </aside>

      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>

<script is:inline>
(function() {
  // Shared newsletter worker (D1-backed) — same endpoint as gtmepulse, fdepulse, etc.
  var SIGNUP_URL = 'https://newsletter-subscribe.rome-workers.workers.dev/subscribe';

  function showSuccess(form) {
    while (form.firstChild) form.removeChild(form.firstChild);
    var msg = document.createElement('p');
    msg.className = 'nl-form__success';
    msg.textContent = "You're in. Look for issue 48 next Wednesday.";
    form.appendChild(msg);
  }

  document.querySelectorAll('.nl-form').forEach(function(form) {
    form.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      var emailInput = form.querySelector('input[type="email"]');
      var btn = form.querySelector('button[type="submit"]');
      var email = (emailInput.value || '').trim();
      if (!email || email.indexOf('@') === -1) {
        emailInput.focus();
        return;
      }
      var orig = btn.textContent;
      btn.textContent = 'Subscribing…';
      btn.disabled = true;

      fetch(SIGNUP_URL, {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
        body: JSON.stringify({ email: email, list: 'gtm-triggers-weekly', source: 'subagentgtm-sample' })
      })
      .then(function(r) { return r.json(); })
      .then(function(data) {
        if (data && (data.success || data.ok)) {
          if (typeof gtag === 'function') {
            gtag('event', 'newsletter_signup', { event_category: 'engagement', event_label: 'gtm-triggers-weekly-sample' });
          }
          showSuccess(form);
        } else {
          btn.textContent = orig;
          btn.disabled = false;
        }
      })
      .catch(function() {
        btn.textContent = orig;
        btn.disabled = false;
      });
    });
  });
})();
</script>

<style>
  /* ============================================
     Layout
     ============================================ */
  .sample-section {
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .sample-back {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .sample-back:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  .sample-back__arrow { transition: transform 0.15s; }
  .sample-back:hover .sample-back__arrow { transform: translateX(-3px); }

  /* ============================================
     Issue container
     ============================================ */
  .issue {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--surface-2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Masthead */
  .issue__head {
    padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-12) var(--space-8);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-2);
  }

  .issue__masthead {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-6);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .issue__masthead-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .issue__masthead-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .issue__masthead-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .issue__masthead-right {
    text-align: right;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .issue__num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .issue__date {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .issue__intro {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .issue__intro-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .issue__intro-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .issue__intro-body strong {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ============================================
     Issue sections
     ============================================ */
  .issue__section {
    padding: var(--space-10) var(--space-12);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-2);
  }

  .issue__section:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }

  .issue__section-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .issue__section-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .issue__section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .issue__section-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6);
  }

  .issue__section-caption {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: var(--space-6) 0 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .issue__section-caption strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* ============================================
     Company rows
     ============================================ */
  .rows {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--space-4) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--surface-2);
  }

  .row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .row__main {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .row__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 17px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .row__name::before {
    content: "/ ";
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .row__note {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .row__meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 4px;
    text-align: right;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .row__stage {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .row__stat {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ============================================
     Bar chart
     ============================================ */
  .bars {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .bars__row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr 56px 56px;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .bars__label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .bars__track {
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bars__fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .bars__pct {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .bars__delta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-align: right;
  }

  /* ============================================
     Conversion bridge
     ============================================ */
  .bridge {
    margin: var(--space-6) 0 0;
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-6);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.06);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .bridge__label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .bridge__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .bridge__body em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .bridge__body a {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding-bottom: 1px;
  }

  /* ============================================
     Stack list
     ============================================ */
  .stacklist {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .stacklist li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--muted);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .stacklist__strike {
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: line-through;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1.5px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .stacklist__arrow {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 var(--space-2);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .stacklist__add {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .stacklist__note {
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* ============================================
     Featured (Trigger of the Week)
     ============================================ */
  .featured {
